<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>About Us - Kisan Sahayak</title>
    <!-- Boxicons for icons -->
    <link href="https://unpkg.com/boxicons@2.1.4/css/boxicons.min.css" rel="stylesheet" />
    <style>
        /* Base & Reset */
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }
        html {
            scroll-behavior: smooth; /* Enables smooth scrolling */
        }
        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            background: #121212;
            color: #E0E0E0;
            line-height: 1.6;
            overflow-x: hidden;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            min-height: 100vh;
        }

        /* Navigation */
        .navbar {
            width: 100%;
            background: rgba(18, 18, 18, 0.9);
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
            box-shadow: 0 0 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, .5);
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 15px 50px;
            position: fixed;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            z-index: 1000;
            transition: background 0.3s, backdrop-filter 0.3s;
        }

        .navbar:hover {
            background: rgba(18, 18, 18, 1);
            backdrop-filter: blur(0);
        }

        .navbar .logo-container {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .navbar .logo {
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #BB86FC;
            margin-left: 10px;
        }

        .navbar .logo-image {
            width: 40px;
            height: 40px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            border: 2px solid #fff;
        }

        .navbar ul {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            list-style: none;
        }

        .navbar ul li {
            margin-left: 20px;
            position: relative;
        }

        .navbar ul li a {
            font-size: 16px;
            color: #E0E0E0;
            padding: 8px 12px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            transition: color 0.3s, background 0.3s;
            text-decoration: none; /* Remove underline */
        }

        .navbar ul li a:hover {
            color: #121212;
            background: #BB86FC;
        }
        
        /* Header */
        header {
            padding: 20px;
            background: rgba(51, 51, 51, 0.7); /* Dark grey with opacity */
            color: white;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: bold;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
            margin-top: 60px; /* Offset for fixed navbar */
        }

        /* Container */
        .container {
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 20px auto;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        .section {
            background-color: #1E1E1E;
            margin: 20px 0;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
        }

        h2 {
            color: #BB86FC;
        }

        p {
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #B0B0B0;
        }

        /* Footer */
        .footer {
            background: rgba(51, 51, 51, 0.7); /* Dark grey with opacity */
            color: #E0E0E0;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 5px 20px; /* Make footer thinner */
            position: sticky;
            bottom: 0;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .footer ul {
            list-style-type: none;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .footer ul li {
            margin: 0 10px;
        }

        .footer ul li a {
            color: #E0E0E0;
            text-decoration: none;
            transition: color 0.3s ease;
        }

        .footer ul li a:hover {
            color: #FF6F61; /* Coral color on hover */
        }

        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .footer {
                flex-direction: column;
                text-align: center;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <!-- Navbar -->
    <nav class="navbar">
        <div class="logo-container">
            <img src="/content/arogya.jpg" alt="Logo" class="logo-image">
            <div class="logo">Kisan Sahayak</div>
        </div>
        <ul>
            <li><a href="/home">Welcome</a></li>
            <li><a href="/logout">Logout</a></li>
            <li><a href="/about">About Us</a></li>
            <li><a href="/book">Marked Doctors</a></li>
        </ul>
    </nav>

    <!-- Header -->
    <header>About Us - Empowering Farmers with AI & Healthcare</header>
    
    <!-- Main Content -->
    <div class="container">
        <div class="section">
            <h2>Our Mission</h2>
            <p>We are dedicated to revolutionizing farmer healthcare and crop disease management through AI-powered technology. Our platform provides essential health support to farmers facing skin issues due to prolonged exposure to fertilizers and chemicals. Additionally, we assist farmers in diagnosing crop diseases, ensuring better yields and sustainable farming.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="section">
            <h2>AI-Powered Farmer Health Assistance</h2>
            <p>Farming exposes workers to harmful chemicals and fertilizers, leading to severe skin conditions and health issues. Our AI-driven system allows farmers to upload images of their skin problems and receive an instant diagnosis with possible remedies. We aim to make healthcare accessible and proactive, preventing long-term health risks.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="section">
            <h2>Book Appointments with Nearby Doctors</h2>
            <p>Recognizing the difficulties in accessing healthcare, our platform enables farmers to find and book appointments with the nearest healthcare professionals. This feature ensures that farmers receive timely medical attention without unnecessary travel burdens.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="section">
            <h2>AI-Driven Crop Disease Detection</h2>
            <p>Agricultural productivity is often threatened by various plant diseases. Our AI model helps farmers identify diseases affecting their crops by simply uploading images. Our system suggests remedial measures and preventive solutions, empowering farmers to make informed decisions and protect their harvests.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="section">
            <h2>Latest Government Schemes for Farmers</h2>
            <p>We provide up-to-date information on government policies, financial aid, and agricultural support programs available for farmers. By staying informed, farmers can take advantage of various schemes designed to improve their livelihoods.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="section">
            <h2>Latest News & Updates</h2>
            <p>Farming is constantly evolving with new techniques, policies, and technologies. We keep farmers updated with the latest news, market trends, and scientific advancements to help them adapt to changes and improve their agricultural practices.</p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Footer -->
    <footer class="footer">
        <ul>
            <li><a href="/cookie-settings">Cookie Settings</a></li>
            <li><a href="/privacy-policy">Privacy Policy</a></li>
            <li><a href="/cookie-policy">Cookie Policy</a></li>
            <li><a href="/terms-and-conditions">Terms and Conditions</a></li>
        </ul>
        <p>Kisan Sahayak &copy; 2025. Empowering Farmers with Technology</p>
    </footer>
</body>
</html>